Package fol

Class Substitution

java.lang.Object
fol.Substitution
public class Substitution extends Object
A substitution is a set of bindings of variables to terms. The unify operation returns a substitution and any first-order logic query with variables will return a (possibly empty) set of substitutions.
Author:
heflin
